<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]"><strong>Why RTK Query instead of a separate axios layer?</strong>
You chose Redux Toolkit. RTK Query is built in =E2=80=94 it gives you cachi=
ng, loading states, and cache invalidation for REST calls with zero extra d=
ependencies.</p>
<p class=3D"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading=
-[1.7]"><strong>Why <code class=3D"bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-b=
