Co-locating the Redux slice with its UI feature (e.g. <code class=3D"bg-tex=
t-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-=
wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">features/cart/cartSlice.js<=
